  "text": "Calculations of these refractive index contributions were performed for four carotenoids: the (normalized) absorption spectra of which were derived from the literature, i.e. galloxanthin [CITATION_1] ; 1-carotene [CITATION_2] ; zeaxanthin [CITATION_3] 21] ; and astaxanthin [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . We also calculated the absorptance, A(l), connected to various peak absorbance values, D max , for an object containing galloxanthin, zeaxanthin or astaxanthin.",
